      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Or did they have this unbelievable, incredible fate of being killed?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we had little time to give it any thought because we were kept busy.",
